{"tid":550619,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"[Fuchsia OS] Google 放棄 Linux Kernel，自行研發新核心","createTime":"2018-02-05T02:20:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-09T23:55:32.000Z","uid":1886,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"2db4f767497774f3596bce5c975bd858851bdd20","tid":550619,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T02:20:31.000Z","msg":"去年已傳聞 Google 正在開發一個全新的跨平台系統 Fuchsia OS，用以取代 Android 系統。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://qooah.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/86435487534.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fqooah.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F02%2F86435487534.jpg&h=152bbebb&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n而 Fuchsia OS 其中一個特點，是放棄 Linux 的核心而改自家研發的新核心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。日前外國媒體 9to5google 報導指，Fuchsia OS 團隊成員 Raph Levien 介紹指他們正開發可用於 Fuchsia OS 和一切桌面平台的文本/代碼編輯器 Xi。<br />\n<br />\n根據這位成員介紹，Xi 的最大特點是效能優先、擴展性極強，因而背後的計算方法、結構性挑戰也很高，所以 Fuchsia OS上的代碼一定要運行快，更指會不惜一切代價。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://qooah.com/2018/02/02/google-fuchsia-os-news/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fqooah.com%2F2018%2F02%2F02%2Fgoogle-fuchsia-os-news%2F&d=wki6ITxkegJeqrB7EpOSB1zEg0sy7MJ6GkP0ogsbSqo%3D&h=72bfa03a\" target=\"_blank\">https://qooah.com/2018/02/02/google-fuchsia-os-news/</a>"},{"pid":"39892bb0003f6b464f54d98036138f258b2cb27c","tid":550619,"uid":78429,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T02:29:49.000Z","msg":"錢多得濟"},{"pid":"8b7a5778ca95b70c565d698c34e6bdfd28002d1d","tid":550619,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T02:30:39.000Z","msg":"以Google設定方向來看，預期Fuchsia作業系統將使絕大多數的平台裝置能夠彼此連接互通，進而達成規模更大的開放平台市場。"},{"pid":"00d5eada7b2aa7491eafe5f16c64259cfe03d1b3","tid":550619,"uid":51932,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T02:31:40.000Z","msg":"Xi呢個名好大陸喎"},{"pid":"6331b2ad963d83d6b885d1766ec3b53de7872a68",